{"tid":1928276,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"劉俊謙：進化先要自我推翻","createTime":"2020-03-16T09:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T07:30:16.000Z","uid":70063,"like":64,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"99f0e58981e05f71f7113ecdd860ee6353bdba41","tid":1928276,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:44:23.000Z","msg":"剛獲得金像獎最佳新演員提名，劉俊謙卻曾經對鏡頭有厭惡感，不願意跟鏡頭談情說愛，明明當時拍攝經驗尚淺，這種想法源於自尊心和不理解，「有人認為，人建立得愈多會阻礙學習，其實絕非必然，可能年輕時會把學到的理論視為唯一。」他現在不停要推翻昨天的我，年輕是一個階段，卻不可能是糊弄一輩子的擋箭牌。<br />\n<br />\n在腦中翻箱倒櫃，他把厭惡源頭歸究於廣告拍攝的經驗，不時要遷就燈光和鏡頭，有時對手更不在眼前。龐大的自尊心是年輕人的必經心態，他也不例外，導致難以虛心地學習。這時他遇到陳曙曦導演，「他常說：『你以為』，他是很重要的老師，讓我不斷自省。」後來，為他帶來香港小劇場獎最佳男主角的《天邊外》，正是陳曙曦導演的作品。一邊把自尊換來思考，一邊在拍攝現場的重播片段中，他看到自己四肢和五官的不自在，間接顯示對鏡頭的陌生感。<br />\n<br />\n舞台劇演員需要擴張肢體，拉緊與觀眾的距離，電視和電影的鏡頭卻可以捕捉微小處，「我發覺偏執都源於太聚焦自己身上，當眼睛環顧四周，身邊都是靈感。」於是他嘗試去閱讀導演、佈景的設計和心思，休息時遠離電話，了解燈光和場內細節，試探可供他探索的空間有多大、底線有多遠，「你知道得愈多，你會愈自在，你可以容許自己有不知道的空間。但如果真的甚麼都不知道，就沒空間讓自己不知道了。」<br />\n<br />\n因為沿用熟悉的《教束》班底，自言對工作挑剔的他參演了ViuTV的劇集《二月廿九》，飾演神聖幾何學會會長余家聰，遇上擁有穿越能力的吳海昕。情節、對白、構思他均覺有趣，於是爽快接下，「我覺得現在電視觀眾想細味多一點，以前大家都看無線長大，老實說他們現在的作品真的乏味。」他也追看過《美味天王》、《刑事偵緝檔案》、《壹號皇庭》，但時代變了，可以輕易接觸到Netflix和HBO，誰還需要死守那個充滿情意結的一號台？「當然仍然有觀眾不喜歡用腦思考，但大多人不再期待只能拌飯的劇情。」要把香港市場、製作規模和成本如此比較，現階段未免太強人所難，但他深信需要消化的創作是大趨勢。把流質食品灌進觀眾喉嚨，只會養出一群直腸直肚、營養不良之士，長久下去，也許機能會退化至吞一口好東西都吃不消。<br />\n<br />\n舞台劇出身的他，去年終於集齊舞台劇、電視劇及電影的經驗。Benedict Cumberbatch、Kevin Spacey等無數的歐美演員都不時跨界別演出，他卻留意到香港無論是觀眾還是行內人士都把三個界別安放在框架中，甚至仍然在舞台劇和演技誇張之間劃上等號，「通常只有兩個原因，一是遇上演技欠佳的舞台劇演員，二是不理解現代舞台劇的真實模樣。」媒介各有可取，他希望成為帶頭的一群，拉近三者間的分野。把媒介的標籤撕走，讓演員回歸演員的純粹，「演員要像水，不同的劇和班底像模子，如果成了水，可以注入任何形態之內。」<br />\n<br />\n現在的劉俊謙擁有回望的胸襟，甚至能理解年輕人的自尊。作為八十後，他自視為曾輕撫香港那美好尾巴的上一輩人，眼見九十後至零零後自出娘胎便呼吸著變了質的空氣，自尊成了他們唯一的心靈依靠，「甚麼都沒擁有，唯有自己去追求意義，沒好的基礎，就自己建立一個基礎。他們要創造新世界的時候，必須去相信自己那一套。」他欣賞年輕人，同時也感到憂心。相信自己是一把雙面刃，如果過於相信則導致自尊心壯大，沒有被摧毀的可能性。一旦摧毀，人生便瓦解。"},{"pid":"139b57cad27184c08c616398a204af2832398b0e","tid":1928276,"uid":70063,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"他們常說的博盡無悔雖勇氣可嘉，但他習慣存疑，也保留可走動的空間，「年輕人要繼續保留信念，同時要反問，假設相信的事不是百份百正確該怎麼辦？」手持一副撲克牌，默默守候著完美的同花順，其實四條、夫佬同樣夠贏，只執著一個可行性，一個不小心便會浪費了一手好牌，輸個清光，「推翻是一個進化的過程，不代表尷尬，不代表曾相信的事不正確。」<br />\n<br />\n和繪畫不同，畫家和畫作的關係較抽離，而演員和演技則以一體呈現。念演藝學院時他想過中途退出，師長、師兄姐，甚至師弟妹的三言兩語令他質疑自己良久，覺得自己跟垃圾無異。他笑言這種自我評價在紛亂社會中甚為普遍，大家都是命運共同體，正面對同樣命題，「我想告訴他們，我也是垃圾，大家一起做垃圾吧，不要緊。」大家都是垃圾，實在不用分那麼細。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://jet.my-magazine.me/article/detail/interview/11315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjet.my-magazine.me%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2Finterview%2F11315&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebSWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=5656bbb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jet.my-magazine.me/article/detail/interview/11315</a>"},{"pid":"da5e2e91d5fb3fa4296c375ac7e439b535926469","tid":1928276,"uid":283908,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"「我想告訴他們，我也是垃圾，大家一起做垃圾吧，不要緊。」大家都是垃圾，實在不用分那麼細。"},{"pid":"e551930c13ef4a96f88ff13237bc618c5f6f30f0","tid":1928276,"uid":202553,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"同意 影視劇的確唔使拉得咁遠<br />\n好演員應該駕馭到唔同表演方式<br />\n亦需要嗮呢3種表演方式<br />\n<br />\nbtw 以前因為TVB所以isolate咗「視」呢塊拼圖<br />\n其實對成個文化界真係好大毒害"},{"pid":"8eaa5c7bb680a13a30dff081255f735032147816","tid":1928276,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"生不逢時"},{"pid":"208e53a30955ac67382edd50e457df37fe85c76f","tid":1928276,"uid":79749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eaa5c7bb680a13a30dff081255f735032147816","tid":1928276,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"生不逢時"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83070f0b816a35f0fa18402d7b66bb034ed14833","tid":1928276,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:42:49.000Z","msg":"殺死往日的自我"},{"pid":"dab31441ff0de0ba90a6761a26b462af04a42f8b","tid":1928276,"uid":1130,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqbjs4G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhqbjs4G.gif&h=df635914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NqJJUKN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNqJJUKN.gif&h=00722c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47HR3C4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47HR3C4.gif&h=87fdebdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uc0sBX8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuc0sBX8.gif&h=979d20e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNeMSwr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNeMSwr.gif&h=89deb0f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7deff9d74c3526a3233471ac22f63bfee4399dd7","tid":1928276,"uid":200249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8609c2c6e3877b92599157a76be04070f43ad51f","tid":1928276,"uid":246962,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"舞台劇演員好多都好戲，但轉去拍電視/電影而又俾到演技出神入化的感覺我的，只有兩位，一個潘燦良，另一個劉俊謙"},{"pid":"6e3fa26b08759acdebc601ba396929bdd0716258","tid":1928276,"uid":2811,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:01:14.000Z","msg":"詹瑞文真係接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5fab03d7b324766884380a746c7828afbda08f","tid":1928276,"uid":40607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:05:56.000Z","msg":"睇好佢"},{"pid":"12a97113e06a0ff06e563cfeaf12c4bf655ef5ad","tid":1928276,"uid":134794,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n舞台劇、話劇係對住觀眾做戲<br />\n觀眾即時有反應<br />\n電視電影係對住鏡頭做戲<br />\n差好撚遠喎"},{"pid":"fff98326b9fbc49168b1e2d86c269a42befe8db0","tid":1928276,"uid":187368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"靚仔又好戲 真係難得<br />\n睇好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24ac440d5034badfa3a195bd4464a4589a2e5ef","tid":1928276,"uid":162406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"89年嘅肥媽同 19年自我推翻嘅肥媽 <br />\n算唔算係自我推翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：尻屎"},{"pid":"0255f8a9829a892e8de3d34f27a8cda06919bc16","tid":1928276,"uid":37396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"好靚仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d20daea3775517a9cf4466ca968b59028197a33","tid":1928276,"uid":246962,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"0255f8a9829a892e8de3d34f27a8cda06919bc16","tid":1928276,"uid":37396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"好靚仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ex7e9vj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEx7e9vj.jpg&h=6715c882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實佢笑得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫咗幾隻字講佢，獻醜了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《論演員--兩代舞台劇王子》<br />\n<br />\n與其話劉俊謙是「另一個周潤發」（by 張婉婷導演），筆者更覺得他會是另一個潘燦良。二人除了出身和經歷相若外，最重點是他們同樣擁有極細膩和全面的演技以及廣闊的戲路，筆者甚至覺得前者有青出於藍之勢，他們這種舞台劇演員的特質其實在電影和電視演員身上並不多見。<br />\n<br />\n可能潘和劉的知名度遠遠不及電影界的天皇巨星，但可以肯定兩位都是真正的演員，選擇角色上不會給自己太多限制，所以觀眾會見到潘燦良在電影《逆流大叔》中成為核突麻甩的凸腩中坑黃淑儀，也會見到劉俊謙在電視劇《未來還未來》中成為滿面暗瘡的大陸仔阿俊 -- 對，他們是「成為」了角色，演員和角色已融為一體。在較弱的明星光環下，或許他們演戲上就能夠去得更「盡」，發揮演技的機會自然無彊界。<br />\n<br />\n長江後浪推前浪，人到中年的潘燦良可能終有一日會退下來，電影圈的中佬巨星都一樣，願劉俊謙以至更多才能突出的年輕男演員能更加發光發亮，把前人所教授的承傳下去。"},{"pid":"9e3bc79dfb24af0d719ecca041a39a240c941f14","tid":1928276,"uid":64953,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"又高又大隻又靚仔又好演技<br />\n我係仔都出哂水<br />\n利申 非基"},{"pid":"4da4b4da7d6c05c66046e3330cf871996ac21ce5","tid":1928276,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"加油謙謙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c099eeebf25ea71b5901fd416209f1c6c4f8d041","tid":1928276,"uid":1130,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXiNLcn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXiNLcn.gif&h=47f18f10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"209b067a1fb8efc819a172fb559992d0aaca17fd","tid":1928276,"uid":339397,"like":1,"dislike":0